2025-09-05PCHMuseums ActAppointment of the trustee of the Board of Trustees of the Canadian Museum of Immigration at Pier 21Approval of the appointment by the Minister of Canadian Heritage of Vinita Savani of Richmond Hill, Ontario, to be a trustee of the Board of Trustees of the Canadian Museum of Immigration at Pier 21, to hold office during pleasure for a term of four years, effective September 29, 2025, in the place of Mona Kumar, whose term will expire.N/A
subject: Appointment of the trustee of the Board of Trustees of the Canadian Museum of Immigration at Pier 21
precis: Approval of the appointment by the Minister of Canadian Heritage of Vinita Savani of Richmond Hill, Ontario, to be a trustee of the Board of Trustees of the Canadian Museum of Immigration at Pier 21, to hold office during pleasure for a term of four years, effective September 29, 2025, in the place of Mona Kumar, whose term will expire.
